modShortDescription: This mod allows you to fill up your generator tank which is huge and leave it be for a long time since it consumes fuel at a reduced pace.
modDescription:
This mod allows you to fill up your [generator](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-electricity/) tank which is huge and leave it be for a long time since it consumes fuel at a reduced pace.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iN8Y1BO2EF90oui2bh_Ulpd9D1y2FrPD/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/21494-alucards-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Noisy Pants](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/noisy-pants/)
